<div type="Textteil" subtype="m" n="171">
<head>*m</head>
<l n="*m 171.01">- daz ist <seg type="große_Variante" n="a1">ein</seg> unsüeze arbeit -,</l>
<l n="*m 171.02">dem sullet ir helfe sîn bereit.</l>
<l n="*m 171.03"><seg type="kleine_Variante" n="a2">wenne</seg> <corr type="Emendation">i</corr>r de<corr type="Emendation">m</corr> t<corr type="Emendation">u</corr>o<corr type="Emendation">t k</corr>umbers buoz,</l>
<l n="*m 171.04">sô nâhet iu der gotes gruoz.</l>
<l n="*m 171.05">ime ist noch &#x2020;wurst&#x2020; danne die gênt</l>
<l n="*m 171.06">nâch <seg type="große_Variante" n="a2">br<corr type="Emendation">ô</corr>te</seg>, <seg type="große_Variante" n="b1">al</seg> dâ diu venster stênt.</l>
<l n="*m 171.07">ir sullet bescheidenlîche</l>
<l n="*m 171.08">sîn arm und rîche,</l>
<l n="*m 171.09">wan <seg type="kleine_Variante" n="a2">wâ</seg> der hêrre gar vertuot,</l>
<l n="*m 171.10">daz ist niht hêrrenlîcher muot.</l>
<l n="*m 171.11">samene<corr type="Emendation">t</corr> er aber <seg type="große_Variante" n="a1">schatz</seg> <seg type="große_Variante" n="b1">ze sêre</seg>,</l>
<l n="*m 171.12">daz sint <seg type="große_Variante" n="a1">ouch</seg> unêre.</l>
<l n="*m 171.13">gebet rehter mâze ir orden.</l>
<l n="*m 171.14">ich bin wol innen worden,</l>
<l n="*m 171.15">daz ir râtes <seg type="große_Variante" n="a2"><seg type="singuläre_Lesart">bedürftic</seg></seg> sît.</l>
<l n="*m 171.16">nû lât der <seg type="große_Variante" n="a2">ungevuoge</seg> <seg type="große_Variante" n="b1">ir</seg> strît.</l>
<l n="*m 171.17">ir sullet niht vil gevrâgen.</l>
<l n="*m 171.18">ouch sol iuch niht betrâgen</l>
<l n="*m 171.19"><seg type="große_Variante" n="a1">bedâhter gegenrede</seg>, <corr type="Emendation">diu g</corr>ê</l>
<l n="*m 171.20">reht, als jenes <seg type="große_Variante" n="a1">vrâgen</seg> stê,</l>
<l n="*m 171.21"><seg type="große_Variante" n="a1">der</seg> <seg type="große_Variante" n="b1">iuch</seg> <seg type="große_Variante" n="c1">dâ</seg> wil mit worten spehen.</l>
<l n="*m 171.22">ir kunnet h&#x0153;ren und sehen,</l>
<l n="*m 171.23">ent<corr type="Emendation">s</corr>eben und <corr type="Emendation">d</corr>r&#x00E6;hen,</l>
<l n="*m 171.24">daz <seg type="große_Variante" n="a1">solte</seg> iuch <seg type="große_Variante" n="b1">witzen</seg> n&#x00E6;hen.</l>
<l n="*m 171.25">lât <seg type="große_Variante" n="b2">erbermde</seg> bî der vrevel sîn.</l>
<l n="*m 171.26"><seg type="singuläre_Lesart">sus</seg> tuot <seg type="singuläre_Lesart">mir</seg> râtes volge schîn:</l>
<l n="*m 171.27">an <seg type="kleine_Variante" n="a2">wem</seg> ir strîtes sicherheit</l>
<l n="*m 171.28"><seg type="kleine_Variante" n="a1">bezalt</seg>, er enhabe iu <seg type="große_Variante" n="a1">solich</seg> leit</l>
<l n="*m 171.29">getân, diu <seg type="kleine_Variante" n="a1">herze<corr type="Emendation">k</corr>umber</seg> wesen,</l>
<l n="*m 171.30">die nemt und lâzet in genesen.</l>
</div>
