<head>*T</head>
<l n="*T 171.01">- daz ist <seg type="große_Variante" n="a1">ein</seg> unsüeze arbeit -,</l>
<l n="*T 171.02">dem sult ir helfe sîn bereit.</l>
<l n="*T 171.03"><seg type="große_Variante" n="a1">wan</seg> <seg type="kleine_Variante" n="a1">swenne</seg> ir dem tuot kumbers buoz,</l>
<l n="*T 171.04">sô nâhet iu der gotes gruoz.</l>
<l n="*T 171.05">im ist noch wirs danne <seg type="große_Variante" n="a1">den</seg>, die gânt</l>
<l n="*T 171.06">nâch <seg type="große_Variante" n="a2">brôte</seg>, dâ diu venster stânt.</l>
<l n="*T 171.07"><seg type="Initiale" subtype="Majuskel">I</seg>r sult bescheidenlîche</l>
<l n="*T 171.08">sîn arm unde rîche,</l>
<l n="*T 171.09">wan <seg type="kleine_Variante" n="a1">swâ</seg> der hêrre gar vertuot,</l>
<l n="*T 171.10">daz <seg type="große_Variante" n="a1">en</seg>ist niht hêrlicher muot.</l>
<l n="*T 171.11">samnet er ab<reg type="Synkope">e</reg>r <seg type="große_Variante" n="a1">schatz</seg> <seg type="große_Variante" n="b3">mêre</seg>,</l>
<l n="*T 171.12">daz sint <seg type="große_Variante" n="a2">grôz</seg> unêre.</l>
<l n="*T 171.13">gebt rehter mâze ir orden.</l>
<l n="*T 171.14">ich bin wol innen worden,</l>
<l n="*T 171.15">daz ir râtes <seg type="große_Variante" n="a1">dürftic</seg> sît.</l>
<l n="*T 171.16">nû lât der <seg type="große_Variante" n="a1">unvuoge</seg> strît.</l>
<l n="*T 171.17"><seg type="Initiale" subtype="Majuskel">I</seg>r sult niht vil gevrâgen.</l>
<l n="*T 171.18">ouch sol iuch niht betrâgen</l>
<l n="*T 171.19"><seg type="große_Variante" n="a2">beidenthalp diu rede</seg>, diu gê</l>
<l n="*T 171.20">rehte, als jen<reg type="Synkope">e</reg>s <seg type="große_Variante" n="a1">vrâgen</seg> stê,</l>
<l n="*T 171.21"><seg type="große_Variante" n="a2">swer</seg> <seg type="große_Variante" n="b2">iuwer</seg> wil mit worten spehen.</l>
<l n="*T 171.22">ir kunnet h&#x0153;ren unde sehen,</l>
<l n="*T 171.23">entseben unde dr&#x00E6;hen,</l>
<l n="*T 171.24">daz <seg type="große_Variante" n="a2">sol</seg> iuch <seg type="große_Variante" n="b2">witze</seg> n&#x00E6;hen.</l>
<l n="*T 171.25">lât <seg type="große_Variante" n="a1">die</seg> <seg type="große_Variante" n="b2">erbermede</seg> bî der vrevel sîn.</l>
<l n="*T 171.26">sus tuot mir râtes volge schîn:</l>
<l n="*T 171.27">an <seg type="kleine_Variante" n="a1">swem</seg> ir strîtes sicherheit</l>
<l n="*T 171.28"><seg type="kleine_Variante" n="a1">bezalt</seg>, ern habiu leit</l>
<l n="*T 171.29">getân, di<corr type="Emendation">u</corr> <seg type="kleine_Variante" n="a2">herzen kumber</seg> wesen,</l>
<l n="*T 171.30">die nemet unde lât in genesen.</l>
</div>
